OL,3,CNHS to open more 'mental health A&Es'
OL,4,Cto relieve pressure on hospitals
OL,6,FThe NHS will open more dedicated
OL,7,Fcentres for people having mental
OL,8,Fhealth emergencies across England in a
OL,9,Fbid to keep those patients out of
OL,10,F"crowded A&Es", the head of NHS
OL,11,FEngland has said.
OL,13,FThe new service will be for patients
OL,14,Fwho present symptoms of a mental
OL,15,Fhealth crisis, such as suicidal
OL,16,Fthoughts or psychosis, The Times
OL,17,Freported.
OL,19,FThey will be staffed by specialist
OL,20,Fdoctors and nurses.
