OL,3,CNHS to open more 'mental health A&Es'
OL,4,Cto relieve pressure on hospitals
OL,6,FTen NHS trusts have already launched
OL,7,Fseparate units for mental health
OL,8,Femergencies, some on the sites of
OL,9,Fexisting A&Es, which are open to walk-
OL,10,Fin patients are well as those referred
OL,11,Fto the service by GPs and police.
OL,13,FThe scheme is expected to be rolled
OL,14,Fout nationally to dozens of locations
OL,15,Fas part of a 10-year NHS plan to be
OL,16,Fpublished this summer by the Labour
OL,17,Fgovernment, according to the newspaper.
