OL,3,CNHS to open more 'mental health A&Es'
OL,4,Cto relieve pressure on hospitals
OL,6,FPatients attending emergency services
OL,7,Fwith mental health symptoms are twice
OL,8,Fas likely to wait 12 hours or more
OL,9,Fthan other patients, a 2022 report
OL,10,Ffrom The Royal College of Emergency
OL,11,FMedicine found.
OL,13,FThe new mental health units will seek
OL,14,Fto reduce the waiting time for mental
OL,15,Fhealth patients and avoid the
OL,16,Fovercrowding of A&E departments amid a
OL,17,F"corridor care" crisis and pressure on
OL,18,Fother emergency services, including
OL,19,Fpolice.
