OL,3,CNHS to open more 'mental health A&Es'
OL,4,Cto relieve pressure on hospitals
OL,6,FIn November 2023, the Metropolitan
OL,7,FPolice, the country's largest force,
OL,8,Fannounced its officers would not
OL,9,Fattend mental health call-outs where a
OL,10,Fhealthcare professional is more
OL,11,Fappropriate.
OL,13,FClaire Murdoch, the NHS national
OL,14,Fdirector for mental health, told the
OL,15,Fnewspaper: "I would certainly hope to
OL,16,Fsee these mental health A&Es across
OL,17,Fthe country over the next decade."
